  "heading_path": "GPT 中文语言风格全域重整报告：以 MD/TEX 学术成文为核心 / 板块一：模型聊天语言风格库（次要留档） / 1.4 逻辑特征：过程链比观点链更重要",
  "intensity": "STRUCTURAL",
  "line_count": 12,
  "masked_text": "[[PROTECTED:F00001-P00090:059f8bb5896f]]\n聊天语言的默认逻辑不是[[PROTECTED:F00001-P00091:bba2cbdc4b04]]，而是：\n\n1. 明示正在采取的动作：[[PROTECTED:F00001-P00092:aca42deab298]]、[[PROTECTED:F00001-P00093:0a5bea76cff4]]。\n2. 给出新发现：[[PROTECTED:F00001-P00094:47279c4f14bb]]、[[PROTECTED:F00001-P00095:5cfc3421f19f]]、[[PROTECTED:F00001-P00096:a77d2b0fbaee]]。\n3. 解释发现：[[PROTECTED:F00001-P00097:1e94ce07d80b]]、[[PROTECTED:F00001-P00098:3f3fbe9aec8e]]。\n4. 提供验证或限制：[[PROTECTED:F00001-P00099:cef4c4920d5b]]、[[PROTECTED:F00001-P00100:3eadf7a929f4]]、[[PROTECTED:F00001-P00101:5e8b5055ddcc]]、[[PROTECTED:F00001-P00102:2d6edd228be6]]。\n5. 交代下一步：[[PROTECTED:F00001-P00103:86dd4369ea09]]、[[PROTECTED:F00001-P00104:75b93dc4026a]]、[[PROTECTED:F00001-P00105:15a1214b9c65]]。\n\n这是一种以执行可见性为中心的逻辑。用户获得的不只是答案，也是在获得[[PROTECTED:F00001-P00106:de564105e064]]的状态估计。\n\n",
